{
  "name": "PE-01: Central Activity Logger",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "sticky-overview-001",
      "name": "Workflow Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -400,
        -100
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 4,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 380,
        "content": "## \ud83c\udfaf PE-01: Central Activity Logger\n### Performance Engine Foundation\n\n**Purpose:** Receive webhooks from ALL automations and store activity data.\n\n**What this does:**\n1. Receives POST webhooks from all system workflows\n2. Validates required fields (client_id, system_number, action_type)\n3. Looks up client benchmarks from Clients sheet\n4. Calculates estimated value based on action type\n5. Enriches data with timestamps and system names\n6. Stores activity in Activity_Log sheet\n7. Triggers daily summary update\n\n**Endpoint:** `/webhook/maxxam-activity-log`\n\n**After Import - You Must:**\n1. Connect Google Sheets credentials\n2. Paste your Sheet URL in both Google Sheets nodes\n3. Update the webhook URL in 'Trigger Daily Summary' node\n\n**MAXXAM AI | Food Truck Implementation**\n**Version:** 1.1 | **Created:** 2026-01-03"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-webhook-001",
      "name": "Webhook Setup Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -50,
        -50
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 6,
        "width": 280,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### \ud83d\udce5 Step 1: Webhook Trigger\n\nAll system workflows POST to this endpoint.\n\n**URL:** Your n8n URL + `/webhook/maxxam-activity-log`"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "webhook-trigger-001",
      "name": "Activity Log Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "position": [
        0,
        100
      ],
      "webhookId": "maxxam-activity-log",
      "parameters": {
        "path": "maxxam-activity-log",
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "responseCode": 200,
        "responseData": "allEntries",
        "options": {
          "rawBody": false
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-validate-001",
      "name": "Validation Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        200,
        -50
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 280,
        "height": 120,
        "content": "### \u2705 Step 2: Validate Payload\n\nChecks for required fields:\n- `client_id` (required)\n- `system_number` (0-9)\n- `action_type` (required)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "validate-payload-001",
      "name": "Validate Required Fields",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "position": [
        250,
        100
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "options": {},
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose"
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "check-client-id",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "isNotEmpty"
              },
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.body?.client_id || $json.client_id || '' }}",
              "rightValue": ""
            },
            {
              "id": "check-action-type",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "isNotEmpty"
              },
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.body?.action_type || $json.action_type || '' }}",
              "rightValue": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "typeVersion": 2
    },
