      "parameters": {
        "color": 5,
        "width": 350,
        "height": 220,
        "content": "### \ud83d\udcb0 Step 6: Calculate Value\n\n**Value Types:**\n- `captured_revenue` - Actual recorded revenue\n- `estimated_revenue` - Projected value\n- `pipeline_value` - Future potential\n- `time_saved` - Hours \u00d7 rate\n- `cost_avoided` - Prevented losses\n- `recovered_revenue` - Win-back value\n\n**Key Actions:**\n- order_taken, quote_accepted\n- call_answered, lead_captured\n- review_received, post_published\n- reactivation_converted"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
