    {
      "id": "sticky-setup-001",
      "name": "Setup Instructions",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -400,
        300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 6,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 350,
        "content": "## \ud83d\udccb Setup Instructions\n\n### 1. Create Google Sheet\nCreate a new Google Sheet named: **MAXXAM Performance Engine**\n\n### 2. Create Required Sheets (tabs)\n\n**Tab 1: Activity_Log** - Rename Sheet1 to this\nIn Row 1, add these column headers:\n`timestamp, client_id, client_name, system_number, system_name, automation_name, action_type, action_detail, quantity, estimated_value, value_type, conversion_status, source_platform, reference_id, metadata, calculation_method, received_at`\n\n**Tab 2: Clients** - Click + to add new tab\nIn Row 1, add these column headers:\n`client_id, client_name, avg_order_value, avg_catering_value, missed_call_lost_sale_rate, sms_response_to_sale_rate, catering_close_rate, qualified_lead_value, hourly_rate, review_value_5star, review_value_4star, review_value_other, active`\n\n### 3. After Import - Configure Nodes\n\n**For BOTH Google Sheets nodes:**\n1. Click on the node\n2. Click 'Credential to connect with' \u2192 Select or create Google Sheets OAuth2\n3. In 'Document' field \u2192 Select 'By URL'\n4. Paste your Google Sheet URL\n5. The Sheet name should auto-populate\n\n### 4. Copy Your Sheet URL\nIt looks like: `https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ABC123xyz/edit`"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sticky-test-001",
      "name": "Test Payload",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -400,
        680
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "color": 7,
        "width": 500,
        "height": 280,
        "content": "## \ud83e\uddea Test Payload\n\nUse this sample payload to test the webhook:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"client_id\": \"lafamilia\",\n  \"system_number\": 3,\n  \"automation_name\": \"S3-01 Goodcall Order Processor\",\n  \"action_type\": \"order_taken\",\n  \"action_detail\": \"Phone order via Goodcall AI\",\n  \"quantity\": 1,\n  \"source_platform\": \"goodcall\",\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"order_total\": 45.50,\n    \"items\": [\"Taco Platter\", \"Horchata\"],\n    \"customer_phone\": \"+1555123456\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Expected Result:** Logs activity with estimated_value = 45.50 (from metadata.order_total)"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    }
  ],
